dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Pacifico Mountain and Palmdale (south half) quadrangles, Los Angeles County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck. Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by soundings. "Prepared in cooperation with the U.S. Forest Service, Angeles National Forest; California Dept. of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; and the U.S. Geological Survey." "Theodore Off Honorary Map." "First printing, April 2001". Includes quadrangle location map, and index to sources of geology and topography. Includes bibliographical references.
dc_creator_sm: Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. Geological Foundation
